;; Supported cgi-functions:
;; g=110  goto-line
;; s=str  search string
;; q=word occur word
;; x=     dired-x
;; 
;; For some cases, mode-specific commands may be desired.
;; See `snap-play-cgi' and `snap-play:help-mode:' for example.

